column5: After a bit had the chance to get out today (couple hours) and hit this 29in Pike. Tried the timer thing, but I guess it's the angle of the dangle  .  Sooooo...
Sweet Bill!!  I just put it up on our Team 2 Entry board, Thanks bud, nice fish!!  Joey
Great to see some pics from you .  MTP
Nice size pike, always fun to catch.
